org.metacsp.multi.spatial.blockAlgebra

Class BlockConstraintSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.metacsp.framework.ConstraintSolver
      • org.metacsp.framework.multi.MultiConstraintSolver
        • org.metacsp.multi.spatial.blockAlgebra.BlockConstraintSolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BlockConstraintSolver
extends MultiConstraintSolver
    This class represents Block Algebra constraints. Each constraint represents three dimension Allen relations between spatial entities. In rectangle Algebra, each spatial entity is restricted to be an axis parallel bounding box.
    Author:
    Iran Mansouri
